# ğŸ¨ Phase 4.1: Component Inventory
> UI building blocks for Edumynt Web App â€” based on **shadcn/ui** + Tailwind CSS

-----
## âœ… Button Variants
- `PrimaryButton` â€“ main CTAs like "Enroll", "Start Test"
- `SecondaryButton` â€“ less urgent actions like "Learn More"
- `GhostButton` â€“ minimal actions (used in headers, cards)
- `DestructiveButton` â€“ delete, unsubscribe
- `LoadingButton` â€“ handles isLoading state + spinner
- `IconButton` â€“ icon-only buttons (e.g., settings, AI, close)
-----
## âœ… Input Components
- `TextInput` â€“ login, ask AI, forms
- `Textarea` â€“ notes, AI, discussions
- `PasswordInput` â€“ with visibility toggle
- `SearchInput` â€“ courses, tests, notes
- `Select / Dropdown` â€“ filters, sort, settings
- `RadioGroup` â€“ MCQ, quiz config
- `Checkbox` â€“ bulk selects, preferences
- `Slider` â€“ font size or video speed
- `Switch` â€“ dark mode, focus mode
-----
## âœ… Cards
- `CourseCard` â€“ shows title, image, progress, CTA
- `LessonCard` â€“ inside course structure
- `TestCard` â€“ title, score, time, action
- `NoteCard` â€“ for ebook/note previews
- `UserCard` â€“ comments, leaderboard
- `MediaCard` â€“ file type, name, usage
-----
## âœ… Layout Components
- `AppShell` â€“ header, sidebar, content, bottom nav
- `SidebarPanel` â€“ used in Lesson/Test pages (tabs: Lessons, Comments, Notes)
- `PageHeader` â€“ title + actions like edit, export
- `EmptyState` â€“ fallback view when nothing exists yet
- `StickyFooterBar` â€“ submit, mark done, continue buttons
-----
## âœ… Utility Components
- `Badge` â€“ for: ğŸ”“ Preview / ğŸ”’ Locked / âœ… Completed / ğŸ§  AI Enabled
- `Progress` â€“ course/test progress bars
- `Alert` â€“ quiz feedback, confirmations
- `Toast` â€“ brief status updates
- `Dialog` â€“ modals for create/edit/confirm
- `Popover` â€“ theme toggle, profile, question hint
- `Tabs` â€“ lesson/test/discussion sections
- `Accordion` â€“ FAQ, expandable lesson groups
- `Tooltip` â€“ hover help, icon descriptions
- `Avatar` â€“ user images (profile, replies)
-----
## âœ… Learning Components (Custom)
- `QuestionBlock` â€“ MCQ and test renderer
- `LessonQuizBox` â€“ embedded quiz in lessons
- `ExplanationBlock` â€“ text + video + "Show similar questions"
- `Flashcard` â€“ (optional) for gamified revision
- `DiscussionThread` â€“ reply thread + reactions + sort
-----
## ğŸ›  Built With
- Based on: **shadcn/ui**, **Tailwind**, **Radix UI Primitives**
- Fully themable with support for `dark` mode and `disabled` state
- Keyboard accessible, ARIA-compliant by default
